      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey can u help me out? i just got this nda from a potential partner and i dont really wanna read the whole thing. can u just tell me the main points i need to know? like whats actually confidential and how long does this thing last? i'll paste it below.\n\n[NDA TEXT START]\nThis Non-Disclosure Agreement (the \"Agreement\") is entered into as of October 12, 2023, by and between Apex Solutions LLC (\"Disclosing Party\") and BrightFlow Ventures Inc. (\"Receiving Party\").\n\n1. Definition of Confidential Information. \"Confidential Information\" shall mean all non-public, proprietary, or sensitive information disclosed by the Disclosing Party, whether oral, written, or electronic, including but not limited to business plans, customer lists, software code, and financial projections.\n\n2. Obligations of Receiving Party. The Receiving Party shall hold the Confidential Information in strict confidence and shall not disclose it to any third party without prior written consent. The Receiving Party shall use the same degree of care to protect the Confidential Information as it uses to protect its own similar confidential information, but in no event less than a reasonable degree of care.\n\n3. Term and Termination. This Agreement shall commence on the Effective Date and shall remain in effect for a period of three (3) years. The obligations of confidentiality with respect to trade secrets shall survive the expiration or termination of this Agreement for as long as such information remains a trade secret under applicable law.\n\n4. Remedies. The Receiving Party acknowledges that any unauthorized disclosure may cause irreparable harm for which monetary damages may be inadequate, and the Disclosing Party shall be entitled to seek injunctive relief.\n[NDA TEXT END]",
      "source": "evaluator",
      "targeted_response_start": "",
